{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the room was put this aside for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was used for many other purposes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Among others, [INAUDIBLE] hiding a generation of communists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The youth in our family, and they were all about eight to 10 years older than I, were very leftist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And throughout the year it was provided for teaching little children Hebrew and prayers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my parents prayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "However, when I was older, I used to go with my fathers grandmother, and I remember that it must have been a special occasion, and I went to the grand synagogue.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This grand synagogue was very old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my uncle, Samuel Cygler, together with another artist who was a painter, painted the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name was Apfelbaum.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they painted the frescoes--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very ancient synagogue, still a wooden--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a wooden structure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course it was burned with 100 people inside-- the first act of German occupation--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sealed off the people and-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh no, this room was divided with a sheet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On one side were women, and on the other side were men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the women were on the side, which throughout the year belonged to a plumber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think that this particular synagogue was held in a very high esteem by my uncles, and by my father, but as a token of respect, they had to go there to set an example to the others.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish community in town was sharply divided into the well-to-do and very poor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Division was-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I am not right in saying that that was sharp-- a sharp division, because it was absorbed-- the poor people were absorbed within community.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of the community took care of the poor one.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
